== 组织图表 ==
威省市政厅由一名市长、一名秘书和24名市议员组成。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.mpsp.gov.my/index.php/en/proposed-bicycle-lanes/general-info/organizational-chart|title=Organizational Chart|website=www.mpsp.gov.my|language=en-gb|access-date=2017-04-29|archive-date=2017-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170717065520/http://www.mpsp.gov.my/index.php/en/proposed-bicycle-lanes/general-info/organizational-chart|dead-url=no}}</ref>市长由[[槟城州政府|槟城州政府]]委任，任期为两年，24名市议员的任期则为一至二年<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.thestar.com.my/metro/community/2016/01/08/newbies-pledge-to-give-their-best-seven-new-councillors-to-serve-from-jan-1-until-dec-31/|title=Newbies pledge to give their best - Community {{!}} The Star Online|website=www.thestar.com.my|access-date=2017-01-01|archive-date=2020-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029020935/https://www.thestar.com.my/metro/community/2016/01/08/newbies-pledge-to-give-their-best-seven-new-councillors-to-serve-from-jan-1-until-dec-31/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而在24名市议员职位中共有21名来自[[希望联盟|希望联盟]]的四个成员党，其中[[民主行动党_(马来西亚)|民主行动党]]有9名、[[人民公正党|人民公正党]]8名、[[国家诚信党|国家诚信党]]和[[土著团结党|土著团结党]]各2名。槟城[[非政府组织|非政府组织]]也获得分配3个市议员名额，以使他们能够参与决策地方政府辖区内的社会事务<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2016/12/28/new-list-of-city-councillors-to-be-tabled-on-jan-4/|title=New list of city councillors to be tabled on Jan 4 - Nation {{!}} The Star Online|access-date=2017-01-01|archive-date=2017-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170101162711/http://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2016/12/28/new-list-of-city-councillors-to-be-tabled-on-jan-4/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

目前市长为自2017年7月3日担任至今的罗查里，在此之前他为威省市议会秘书。同样的市政厅秘书则由原城市服务部主任罗斯娜妮接替罗查里空出的职位。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.thesundaily.my/news/2017/06/30/new-mayor-penang-island-city-council|title=New Mayor for Penang Island City Council|website=www.thesundaily.my|language=en|access-date=2017-06-30|archive-date=2017-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170630091042/http://www.thesundaily.my/news/2017/06/30/new-mayor-penang-island-city-council|dead-url=no}}</ref>

